Package decoworld.model.world.map

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Map
    Represents a single instance of a Map, within a greater Universe.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Array2D<T>
    A helper class to assist with 2 dimensional arrays usage.
    BaseMap
    Represents the base, concrete implementation of a Map.
    ClientMap
    Represents a client-side map instance, with no support for editing.
    MapIO
    Provides methods to read and write map files.
    ServerMap
    Represents a Map that can track server-side changes.
    TeleportTile
    An entity that allows players to teleport inside a map or between worlds.
    Tile
    A type of tile within a BaseMap.
    TileChange
    Represents a tile that has changed on a Map.
    TileSet
    The comprehensive set of Tile that may be used in a BaseMap.
    TileSetIO  
    TileSets
    Provides access to all TileSets stored on the local machine.
